### **3. 21_LogClusterScope**  
**Description:**  
A parser that groups similar log messages, detects bursts, and highlights trending keywords.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogClusterScope - Repetition & Spike Analyzer

LogClusterScope gives you a frequency view of your logs by clustering repeating messages and time-based anomalies.

## Features
- Frequency heatmap  
- Burst detection  
- Keyword pattern matching  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_LogClusterScope.git
cd 21_LogClusterScope
python analyze.py
